Accommodation room nights, rental car days and airline tickets reserved through our services each declined for the year
ended December 31, 2020, compared to the year ended December 31, 2019, due to the COVID-19 pandemic, which drove a
substantial decline in new travel bookings and increased cancellation rates.
Gross bookings resulting from reservations of accommodation room nights, rental car days and airline tickets made
through our agency and merchant models for the years ended December 31, 2020 and 2019 were as follows (numbers may not total
