expected ROIs in our marketing channels. Marketing expenses as a percentage of total revenues decreased for the year ended
December 31, 2020, compared to the year ended December 31, 2019, primarily due to actions we took to reduce our brand and
performance marketing spend in response to the reduced travel demand.
