Approximately 88%, 87% and 87% of the Company's revenues for each of the years ended December 31, 2020, 2019 and
2018, respectively, relates to online accommodation reservation services. Revenue from all other sources of online travel
reservation services and advertising and other revenues each individually represent less than 10% of the Company's total revenues
for each year.
