11.    GOODWILL, INTANGIBLE ASSETS AND OTHER LONG-LIVED ASSETS
 
A substantial portion of the Company's intangible assets and goodwill relates to the acquisitions of OpenTable and
KAYAK.
Goodwill
The changes in the balance of goodwill for the years ended December 31, 2020 and 2019 consist of the following (in
millions): 
 2020 2019
